{"tid":1955982,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國務院宣布明日全國下半旗　為疫情犧牲人士致哀","createTime":"2020-04-03T00:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T02:10:05.000Z","uid":3090,"like":4,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"70b15b9da4e610645c881224c6189a633ac18729","tid":1955982,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T00:45:44.000Z","msg":"在北京，國務院宣布，將於明日舉行全國性哀悼活動，全國和駐外使領館下半旗，為抗擊新型肺炎疫情犧牲烈士和逝世同胞致哀。<br />\n<br />\n公告提到，哀悼活動中由明日10時起，全國人民默哀3分鐘，汽車、火車、船艦鳴笛，防空警報鳴響致哀，全國停止公共娛樂活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518583-20200403.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518583-20200403.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=86a8933f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518583-20200403.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=21d72496\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518583-20200403.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"f34597ed0b1d568dc0d1bfc6d3e89fe6bfb02787","tid":1955982,"uid":258578,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T00:46:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3237f23bef8053a9c3ed22384f07128a808eb5f2","tid":1955982,"uid":74622,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T00:49:34.000Z","msg":"造謠人士改口變做烈士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f5eb9c6db457845c22f0fa75d75e1f71adfa167","tid":1955982,"uid":67468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T00:50:09.000Z","msg":"烈⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯"},{"pid":"60fa35b5b0ab148c23305136bcd5b47f2cdebe94","tid":1955982,"uid":4964,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T00:54:47.000Z","msg":"香港個幾個解放軍冇人記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9e0cbd95b0603712968bd6e3fd16d4d8310e47","tid":1955982,"uid":15